    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;../../assets/images/wiapost/5293-meaning-of-prakriti-in-bhagavad-gita.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;The Meaning of Prakriti in Bhagwat Gita&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;The Meaning of Prakriti in Bhagwat Gita 
    &lt;div id=&#34;the-meaning-of-prakriti-in-bhagwat-gita&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
